        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(a11y): B-1+B-2+B-3 — contrast, focus states, minimum font sizes",
        "body": "## Accessibility Pass\n\n### B-1 — Muted text contrast\n- Raised `--muted` token in default dark theme: `#838387` → `#8b8b94` (5.04→5.63:1 on bg, 4.51→5.04 on elevated surfaces)\n- Raised `--muted-strong` in default dark: `#75757d` → `#898990`\n- Raised `--muted` in openknot dark theme: `#7a7a80` → `#8a8a94` (was 4.31:1 on bg-elevated, now 5.38:1)\n- Raised `--muted-strong` in openknot dark: `#6e6e76` → `#888892`\n- Adjusted light mode `--muted` tokens to maintain safe buffer above 4.5:1\n- All values verified ≥4.8:1 against both `--bg` and `--bg-elevated` (glass surfaces)\n\n### B-2 — Focus-visible states\n- Updated global `:focus-visible` rule in `base.css`: now emits `outline: 2px solid var(--accent)` + `outline-offset: 2px` distinct from any hover style\n- Added `:focus:not(:focus-visible) { outline: none }` to suppress focus ring on mouse click\n- Migrated all `:focus` rules across `config.css`, `components.css`, `chat/tool-cards.css`, `chat/layout.css`, `layout.css`, `workboard.css`, `skill-workshop.css`, `usage.css`, `cron-quick-create.css` → `:focus-visible`\n- Updated paired `:hover:not(:focus)` guards → `:hover:not(:focus-visible)`\n\n### B-3 — Minimum font sizes\n- Lifted all sub-12px `font-size` values to `12px` minimum across all `ui/src/styles/` CSS files\n- Affected: timestamps, metadata labels, badge counters, tool card details, sidebar items, config labels, usage charts, skill workshop elements (136 instances, 8–11px → 12px)\n\nAll changes are CSS-only, zero JS changes.\n\n---\nPart of UI/UX Enhancement Sprint 2.",
